{"tid":1600431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[發夢後保障自己] 記得換衫先走啊！！！","createTime":"2019-09-28T15:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T15:25:10.000Z","uid":273014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"03509075a85bd4ca996ba2582d21c693dbdaeec9","tid":1600431,"uid":273014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:21:12.000Z","msg":"手足們，我今日睇live見到你地好多都直接著件<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色衫離開</span></span></strong>，咁樣<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">風險係好高</span></span></strong>咖，千祈記得要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">換件普通t-shirt</span></span></strong>先好走呀！！我地發夢將近3個月啦，準備定件衫替換係好基本咖，尤其依家D狗巴士又搜、電車又搜，見到你成車都係黑衣人唔截查就奇啦！<br />\n<br />\n可能你會話，佢依家係唔係都截咖啦，但始終一架全黑巴同一架彩色巴相對，肯定前者係大機會被人搜，所以為左保障自己同其他手足（除非逼不得已要逃亡換唔切），唔係都盡量換裝啦！"},{"pid":"49ba64f296db3c6b712f8942a1303a5388584efe","tid":1600431,"uid":238920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"最好抹埋手面,架直昇機有灑螢光粉"},{"pid":"bbc41a870b1803857e7ca7dfe0b7f8173ebf1d30","tid":1600431,"uid":273014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}